                            <comment id="13851543" author="sandermak" created="Wed, 18 Dec 2013 10:06:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;One trivial improvement to the patch would be to allocate an ArrayList of the correct capacity, to avoid resizing overhead:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; List copyComponents = new ArrayList(m_components.size());&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;or even let the list copy itself without for loop in the synchronized block&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt;  List copyComponents = new ArrayList(m_components);&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
